          <dt>代表取締役</dt>
          <dd>猫山ポン太郎</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="p-company-info__row">
          <dt>資本金</dt>
          <dd>1,000,000円</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="p-company-info__row">
          <dt>所在地</dt>
          <dd>〒555-5555 東京都千代田区 ポンビルディング 606</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
      <div class="p-company-info__map">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d25924.77829319612!2d139.7357797726949!3d35.68691680243238!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x60188c0c0b13f54d%3A0xb630953beee48188!2z5p2x5Lqs6YO95Y2D5Luj55Sw5Yy6!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1777801900008!5m2!1sja!2sjp" width="1110" height="400" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="p-company-info__map-link">
        <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/ggB7EYKgcHEMiPNu8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Google mapで見る
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="contact-area" class="p-contact">
    <div class="container l-container">
      <h2 class="c-section-title c-title">
        <span class="c-section-title__main">CONTACT</span>
        <span class="c-section-title__sub">お問い合わせ</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="p-contact__text">WEBサイトの制作のご依頼やお見積りなど、<br class="pc-none">お気軽にご相談ください。</p>
      <div class="c-button-wrap">
        <a href="./contact.html" class="c-button c-button--primary c-button--more">MORE</a>
      </div>
